Introduction
------------

TwitUser is a dataset of language-labeled Twitter messages meant for the
evaluation of automatic approaches to language identification of Twitter messages.
Its preparation and characteristics are described in [1]. If you use this data in your
own research, please cite it as:

@InProceedings{lui-baldwin:2014:LASM,
  author    = {Lui, Marco  and  Baldwin, Timothy},
  title     = {Accurate Language Identification of Twitter Messages},
  booktitle = {Proceedings of the 5th Workshop on Language Analysis for Social Media (LASM)},
  month     = {April},
  year      = {2014},
  address   = {Gothenburg, Sweden},
  publisher = {Association for Computational Linguistics},
  pages     = {17--25},
  url       = {http://www.aclweb.org/anthology/W14-1303}
}

